633
00:37:30,147 --> 00:37:32,149
SHUT UP, IRA.
I WASN'T GOING THROUGH ANYTHING.

634
00:37:32,650 --> 00:37:35,152
I KNOW WHERE THE GUN IS.
WE ALL KNOW WHERE THE GUN IS.
YOU SHOW US EVERY SUMMER.

635
00:37:35,152 --> 00:37:37,655
I THOUGHT WE MIGHT SEE IT
AND, AS YOU CAN SEE,
WE DID !

636
00:37:37,655 --> 00:37:40,658
- WELL, FINE.
  GO PUT IT BACK NOW.
- SORRY, HOLMES.  THE GUN STAYS.

637
00:37:42,660 --> 00:37:45,663
