IS WRONG WITH YOU ?

649
00:38:16,193 --> 00:38:19,196
GIVE IT TO ME.
NO.

650
00:38:19,196 --> 00:38:21,699
I SAID
GIVE IT TO ME.

651
00:38:21,699 --> 00:38:24,201
NO.

652
00:38:24,201 --> 00:38:27,705
I AM SO, SO FUCKING
SICK OF YOU !

653
00:38:28,706 --> 00:38:30,708
