657
00:38:47,725 --> 00:38:51,729
I CAN'T WATCH IT NOW.
GODDAMN IT.

658
00:38:52,229 --> 00:38:55,733
I'M GONNA GO OUT
AND GET CIGARETTES.

659
00:38:56,233 --> 00:38:58,235
WE MONSTERS OWE YOU
A LOT MORE.

660
00:38:58,736 --> 00:39:01,238
YOU HAVE THE CUNNING
OF A BAT.

661
00:39:01,238 --> 00:39:04,241
REMEMBER:
KEEP THE DOOR SHUT.

662
00:39:04,241 --> 00:39:06,243
MAKE SURE
SHE DON'T GET OUT.

663
00:39:06,243 --> 00:39:08,245
I KNOW, I KNOW.

664
00:39:09,246 --> 00:39:12,750
- LEAVE THE REMOTE.
- I'M TAKIN' IT WITH ME.

665
00:39:15,753 --> 00:39:17,755
KING OF THE DICKS.

666
00:39:30,968 --> 00:39:34,972
HOW 'BOUT WE PUT
OUR HEADS TOGETHER,
FIGURE THIS OUT.  GUYS.

667
00:39:38,976 --> 00:39:40,978
WHAT ?

668
00:39:41,479 --> 00:39:43,981
CAN ANYBODY TELL ME
ANYTHING THAT COULD HELP ?

669
00:39:43,981 --> 00:39:49,487
- NOTHIN' WE HAVEN'T ALREADY
  TOLD THE POLICE.
- COPS.  FUCK 'EM.  TELL ME.

670
00:39:49,487 --> 00:39:52,490
UH, WE WERE GOING TO GO
INTO THE CITY,

671
00:39:52,990 --> 00:39:54,492
HIT A COUPLE PARTIES,
 HIT A COUPLE CLUBS,

672
00:39:54,992 --> 00:39:57,495
AND, UH, MAX AND LISA
WERE SUPPOSED TO MEET US
AT MIDNIGHT.

