-[ Charlie ]  WAS THERE
 SOMETHING GOING ON ?

675
00:40:04,969 --> 00:40:07,471
YEAH, WE BEEN TOGETHER
ALMOST A YEAR.
WHAT DOES THAT TELL YOU ?

