706
00:41:59,950 --> 00:42:02,453
JUST PROMISE.

707
00:42:03,954 --> 00:42:05,956
I PROMISE.

708
00:42:07,458 --> 00:42:09,460
HEY.

709
00:42:11,462 --> 00:42:13,464
YOU'RE MY ANGEL.

710
00:42:13,464 --> 00:42:17,468
YOU KNOW THAT,
