00:44:14,084 --> 00:44:17,588
TOO YOUNG FOR KOREA,
 TOO OLD FOR 'NAM.

737
00:44:22,593 --> 00:44:26,096
DR. MENGELE, WHAT HAPPENED ?
CHOP OFF ANOTHER FINGER ?

738
00:44:26,096 --> 00:44:29,600
- NO, WHY ?
