749
00:44:56,126 --> 00:44:59,129
- H-HE'S ALL TIED UP.
  HE CAN'T DO ANYTHING.
- SORRY, LADIES.  THE GUN STAYS.

750
00:44:59,129 --> 00:45:02,633
- BRETT, THE FUCKIN' THING
  IS POINTED RIGHT AT ME.
- THE THING COULD GO OFF.

751
00:45:02,633 --> 00:45:07,137
IRA COULD GET LAID.  WHO CARES.
IF YOU DON'T LIKE IT,
GO IN THE OTHER ROOM.

752
00:45:07,137 --> 00:45:09,139
HEY, CHASE,
COULD YOU HAND ME
THAT PILLOW REAL FAST ?

753
00:45:11,141 --> 00:45:14,645
