THE TABLE AT A SURE THING.

1161
01:10:48,074 --> 01:10:52,578
I DON'T HAVE TO TAKE THIS SHIT.
I'M OUTTA HERE.

1162
01:10:52,578 --> 01:10:56,082
I THOUGHT HE'D NEVER LEAVE.

1163
01:10:56,082 --> 01:10:59,085
YOU'RE 180 OFF ON BRETT.
HE'S A WILD MAN.

1164
01:10:59,085 --> 01:11:02,088
WE'RE IN ATLANTIC CITY,
I HAD TO LOCK HIM IN A ROOM.

1165
01:11:02,088 --> 01:11:04,590
WHAT HAPPENED ?  HE DROPPED
A COUPLE OF QUARTERS
IN THE SLOTS ?

1166
01:11:04,590 --> 01:11:08,094
-[ Charlie Laughs ]
- HUH !  ABOUT 48,000 QUARTERS.

1167
01:11:08,594 --> 01:11:12,598
WE DROVE DOWN TO JERSEY
ON MEMORIAL DAY.

1168
01:11:12,598 --> 01:11:15,101
- LABOR DAY.
- UH--

1169
01:11:15,101 --> 01:11:18,604
WHATEVER.  JUST SHUT UP,
OKAY ?  I'M TRYIN' TO TELL
A STORY HERE.

1170
01:11:19,105 --> 01:11:21,107
- IRA.
- WHAT ?

1171
01:11:21,107 --> 01:11:26,112
YOU CAN'T TELL A STORY HERE.
YOU CAN'T TELL A STORY ANYWHERE.
YOU SCREW IT UP EVERY TIME.

1172
01:11:26,112 --> 01:11:29,115
- NO, I DO NOT.
- YOU'RE DOING IT NOW.

1173
01:11:29,115 --> 01:11:32,618
THAT'S BECAUSE YOU GUYS
INTERRUPT EVERY TIME.
I CAN'T KEEP MY PLACE.

1174
01:11:32,618 --> 01:11:36,122
I FORGET WHERE I WAS.
IF YOU GET THE GODDAMN
STORY STRAIGHT,

1175
01:11:36,122 --> 01:11:38,624
WE WOULDN'T HAVE
TO INTERRUPT YOU TO GET
THE GODDAMN STORY STRAIGHT.

1176
01:11:38,624 --> 01:11:42,628
- WELL, IS SOMEBODY GOING
  TO TELL A STORY ?
- I WAS TELLING THE STORY !

1177
01:11:42,628 --> 01:11:45,631
JUST SHUT THE FUCK UP.
I'LL TELL IT.
YOU FUCK IT UP EVERY TIME.

1178
01:11:46,132 --> 01:11:48,134
IT WAS LABOR DAY, IRA,
LIKE T.K. SAID.

1179
01:11:48,634 --> 01:11:51,637
IT WAS SCORCHIN' OUTSIDE,
IT WAS SO FUCKIN' HOT.
DON'T YOU REMEMBER THAT ?

1180
01:11:51,754 --> 01:11:54,757
THE ROOM WAS FREEZIN' THOUGH.
YOU COULD HANG MEAT IN THIS 
ROOM, IT WAS SO DAMN COLD.

1181
01:11:54,757 --> 01:11:57,760
IT WAS GOOD FOR BUSINESS.
 IT KEEPS YOU AWAKE.

1182
01:11:57,760 --> 01:12:00,263
WE'RE POUNDIN' SAUCE.
FREE BOOZE.
WHAT THEY LOSE ON THAT...

1183
01:12:00,263 --> 01:12:02,265
THEY MAKE UP
ON JOHNNY WALKER JUDGMENT.

1184
01:12:02,265 --> 01:12:05,768
IT'S GETTIN' REALLY LATE.
THE SUN'S ABOUT TO COME UP.
WE'D ALL LOST OUR SHIRTS.

1185
01:12:05,768 --> 01:12:08,771
MAXED OUT THE PLASTIC.
EXCEPT FOR BRETT.

1186
01:12:08,771 --> 01:12:11,274
BRETT'S WINNIN',
LIKE, HUGE.

1187
01:12:13,276 --> 01:12:15,278
THAT'S WHEN IT HAPPENED.

1188
01:12:16,779 --> 01:12:18,781
CHANGING OF THE GUARD.

1189
01:12:19,282 --> 01:12:21,284
[ Man ]
NO-O-O !
[ Coughs ]

1190
01:12:21,284 --> 01:12:24,287
WORD HAD IT THEY BROUGHT
THIS GUY IN FROM VEGAS
AFTER TWO SUICIDES.

1191
01:12:24,287 --> 01:12:28,291
IT'S THE GUY THEY BROUGHT
IN TO COOL THE TABLE DOWN.
YOU KNOW WHAT THEY CALL HIM ?

1192
01:12:28,291 --> 01:12:30,293
HELLO, BOYS !
THE WIDOWMAKER.

1193
01:12:30,793 --> 01:12:33,796
WHAT A LITTLE SHIT
THIS GUY WAS.

1194
01:12:33,796 --> 01:12:36,299
IT'S LIKE THE KID
THAT REMINDS THE TEACHER
ABOUT THE HOMEWORK ASSIGNMENT.

1195
01:12:36,299 --> 01:12:38,801
OH !
WELL, THAT'S THIS KID
GROWN UP.

1196
01:12:40,803 --> 01:12:44,307
ANYWAY, BRETT'S 22 GRAND AHEAD,
SO I FIGURE IT'S SAFE
TO GO TO THE JOHN, RIGHT ?

1197
01:12:44,307 --> 01:12:47,810
WRONG.  GONE FIVE MINUTES,
I COME BACK, HE'S DOWN 12.

1198
01:12:47,810 --> 01:12:51,314
I TRY TO TALK HIM INTO
CHANGING TABLES, BUT HE
TAKES OUT A MARKER.

1199
01:12:51,314 --> 01:12:55,818
YOU FUCKIN' BELIEVE THAT ?
[ Men ]
OH-H-H !

1200
01:12:55,818 --> 01:13:00,823
RIGHT THEN AVERY WALKS UP.
HE'S JUST GOT DONE SWEATIN' OUT
THE GEORGETOWN-MISSISSIPI GAME,

1201
01:13:00,823 --> 01:13:03,826
BUT AT TEN TO ONE,
HE'S COME OUT FIVE GRAND AHEAD.

1202
01:13:04,327 --> 01:13:07,830
HE TAKES ONE LOOK AT THIS LITTLE
WIMP, AND HE DUMPS HIS FIVE Gs
RIGHT ON TOP OF BRETT'S ACTION.

1203
01:13:07,830 --> 01:13:11,834
THESE CLOWNS, THEY'RE GONNA
TAKE THE WIDOWMAKER'S BALLS HOME
AND HIS LUGGAGE WITH ONE HAND.

1204
01:13:11,834 --> 01:13:15,838
SO WHAT DOES
BRETT THE GENIUS DO ?
HE DOUBLES DOWN !

1205
01:13:15,838 --> 01:13:20,343
WIDOWMAKER LOOKED HIM
RIGHT IN THE EYE,
AND HE DREW ONE CARD.

1206
01:13:20,343 --> 01:13:24,230
WHOA-HO-HO-HO-HO !
SORRY !
[ Mock Crying ]

1207
01:13:24,230 --> 01:13:27,233
I'M SORRY.
GIMME THE MONEY !

1208
01:13:27,233 --> 01:13:30,353
THE GUY, HE'S--
HE'S GOT ROCKS
THE SIZE OF RUSHMORE.

1209
01:13:30,353 --> 01:13:35,358
OH, COME ON GUYS !  DON'T LEAVE.
WEREN'T WE JUST HAVIN'
A GOOD TIME ?  COME ON !

1210
01:13:35,358 --> 01:13:39,862
COME ON, COME ON !
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA !
[ Barking, Laughing ]

1211
01:13:39,979 --> 01:13:41,981
AFTERWARDS, BRETT TAKES
HIS LAST 200 BUCKS,

1212
01:13:41,981 --> 01:13:46,486
HE TAKES US ALL OUT FOR STEAKS
THE SIZE OF YOUR FOOT.
[ Charlie ]  WHAT A GUY.

1213
01:13:46,486 --> 01:13:52,492
HE DROPS 20 GRAND, HE AIN'T GOT
MONEY LEFT FOR A BUS TICKET
HOME, HE TAKES YOU FOR STEAKS.

1214
01:13:52,492 --> 01:13:56,496
IT MUST BE NICE
TO HAVE RICH FOLKS.
YOU DON'T KNOW HIS FATHER.

1215
01:13:56,496 --> 01:13:59,499
HE'S GOT THE FIRST NICKEL
HE EVER MADE.

1216
01:13:59,499 --> 01:14:03,002
SO, HOW'S HE GONNA PAY BACK
THE 20 LARGE ?

1217
01:14:03,002 --> 01:14:06,005
THE INTEREST ALONE IS ENOUGH
TO GIVE YOU A NOSEBLEED.

1218
01:14:10,009 --> 01:14:12,645
WHAT ?

1219
01:14:13,146 --> 01:14:15,648
MY ARM, IT'S KILLING ME.

1220
01:14:16,149 --> 01:14:18,151
LOOSEN THE TAPE.
IT'S FALLING OFF.

1221
01:14:21,771 --> 01:14:25,274
SO, YOU KNOW WHAT ?
HOW YA FEELIN' ?

1222
01:14:25,274 --> 01:14:27,777
THAT'S IT.
OOH !  YEAH.
YEAH ?

1223
01:14:30,279 --> 01:14:34,283
COUPLE MINUTES.
TRY TO KEEP IT LEVEL.
OOH, YEAH.

1224
01:14:34,784 --> 01:14:37,787
WHAT ARE YOU DOIN' ?
WHAT THE FUCK ARE YOU DOIN' ?
NO, NO, NO !
HEY !

1225
01:14:38,287 --> 01:14:41,290
- NO !
- YOU FUCKER !  I WAS SITTIN'
  ON A STRAIGHT FLUSH THERE !

1226
01:14:41,290 --> 01:14:44,794
BRETT, WILL YOU RELAX ?  HE
DOESN'T HAVE THE BLOOD PRESSURE
TO WALK AROUND THE ROOM !

1227
01:14:44,794 --> 01:14:48,297
LOOK AT HIM !
WHAT ARE YOU WORRIED ABOUT ?
WE HAD A FUCKIN' PLAN !

1228
01:14:48,297 --> 01:14:50,800
THAT'S WHAT I'M WORRIED ABOUT !
I WANT TO STICK TO THE PLAN !

1229
01:14:50,800 --> 01:14:55,805
- UH, MAYBE THAT'S NOT ALL
  YOU'RE WORRIED ABOUT, HUH ?
- WHAT THE FUCK DOES THAT MEAN ?

1230
01:14:55,805 --> 01:14:58,307
GO AHEAD, T.K.
ASK HIM.

1231
01:14:58,808 --> 01:15:02,311
ASK ME WHAT ?
 ASK ME WHAT ?
GO ON, T.K.  T.K. !

1232
01:15:02,311 --> 01:15:04,814
SHUT UP !
ASK ME WHAT ?

1233
01:15:04,814 --> 01:15:06,816
JUST ANSWER THIS QUESTION,
OKAY ?

1234
01:15:07,316 --> 01:15:12,321
ALL THAT MONEY IN ATLANTIC CITY
THAT YOU LOST-- HOW WERE YOU
GONNA PAY IT BACK ?

1235
01:15:12,321 --> 01:15:17,326
- YEAH, HOW WERE YOU
  GONNA PAY THAT BACK, HUH ?
- NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS.  WHY ?

1236
01:15:17,326 --> 01:15:20,329
WELL, YOU SEE,
IT'S BEEN BROUGHT
TO CHARLIE'S ATTENTION...

1237
01:15:20,329 --> 01:15:23,833
THAT ONE OF US MIGHT BE
IN ON ELISE'S KIDNAPPING.

1238
01:15:25,334 --> 01:15:28,337
[ Laughing ]
WHAT ?
YEAH.
WELL, THAT'S HOW I FELT.

1239
01:15:28,337 --> 01:15:31,340
BUT, YOU KNOW,
MAYBE IT'S NOT THAT CRAZY.

1240
01:15:31,340 --> 01:15:34,343
AND, UH, $20,000
IS A LOT OF MONEY.

1241
01:15:34,343 --> 01:15:37,847
SO, IF YOU HAVE NOTHING
TO HIDE, YOU SHOULD HAVE
NO PROBLEM TELLING US...

1242
01:15:37,847 --> 01:15:40,349
HOW YOU WERE GONNA
PAY IT BACK, RIGHT ?

1243
01:15:40,349 --> 01:15:45,354
IRA, YOU'RE MY FRIEND.
LISTEN:  SHUT THE FUCK UP !
SHUT UP !

1244
01:15:45,354 --> 01:15:47,857
- HE SOUNDS GUILTY TO ME.
- IRA !

1245
01:15:47,857 --> 01:15:49,859
-FUCKIN' FAGGOT !  COME HERE !
- HEY, HEY, HEY !

1246
01:15:49,859 --> 01:15:54,363
HEY, BRETT !  COME ON !
AVERY, AVERY.  OOH.
DON'T TELL ME...

1247
01:15:54,363 --> 01:15:56,365
YOUR BUYIN' INTO THIS FUCKIN'
LOAD OF BULLSHIT !

1248
01:15:56,365 --> 01:15:59,368
HE'S MAKIN' UP STORIES
TO SAVE HIS OWN ASS !

1249
01:15:59,368 --> 01:16:01,871
LOOK, YOU CALM DOWN,
ALL RIGHT ?

1250
01:16:01,871 --> 01:16:05,875
I DON'T THINK THAT
ANYBODY HERE IS INVOLVED IN
ELISE'S KIDNAPPING, ALL RIGHT ?

1251
01:16:06,375 --> 01:16:11,380
BUT I THINK THAT IT
MIGHT BE TIME THAT WE
REVALUATE OUR PLAN.

1252
01:16:11,881 --> 01:16:17,386
WHY ?  THE PLAN'S WORKING, MAN.
HE FUCKING MADE THE CALL.  WHY ?

1253
01:16:18,888 --> 01:16:21,390
I THINK WE SHOULD
JUST LET CHARLIE GO.

1254
01:16:21,390 --> 01:16:23,392
- ME TOO.
- IRA, SHUT THE FUCK UP.

1255
01:16:23,893 --> 01:16:26,395
HE'S NOT DOIN' SO WELL.
WE SHOULD GET HIM TO A HOSPITAL.

1256
01:16:26,395 --> 01:16:30,900
WHAT THE FUCK ?  I LEAVE
THE ROOM, YOU GUYS ROLL OVER
LIKE FIVE-DOLLAR WHORES.

1257
01:16:30,900 --> 01:16:34,904
YOU HAVE A DRINK WITH THE GUY,
NEXT THING YOU KNOW,
HE'S BEST MAN AT YOUR WEDDING.

1258
01:16:34,904 --> 01:16:39,408
WHAT THE FUCK DID HE DO ?
SPRINKLE FAIRY DUST UP
YOUR SKIRTS ?  COME O--

1259
01:16:39,408 --> 01:16:42,411
AVERY.  AVERY !
BUDDY, MAN--

1260
01:16:42,411 --> 01:16:46,415
THIS IS YOUR SISTER'S LIFE
WE'RE TALKIN' ABOUT, MAN.

1261
01:16:46,415 --> 01:16:49,919
WHAT THE FUCK ?
MAN, LOOK AT US.

1262
01:16:49,919 --> 01:16:54,924
WE CUT HIS FUCKIN' FINGER OFF !
MAN, YOU'RE WALKIN' AROUND
WITH A GUN !

1263
01:16:54,924 --> 01:16:58,427
THIS ISN'T US.
WE'RE NO BETTER THAN HE IS.

1264
01:16:58,427 --> 01:17:01,430
TELL ELISE THAT.

1265
01:17:01,430 --> 01:17:04,934
HE HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH ELISE'S KIDNAPPING.
HE HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH IT.

1266
01:17:04,934 --> 01:17:07,436
DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND THAT ?
HE DIDN'T DO ANYTHING !

1267
01:17:07,436 --> 01:17:11,941
IT DOESN'T MATTER !  WHOEVER
DID THE ACTUAL KIDNAPPING--
IT'S A FUCKING TECHNICALITY !

1268
01:17:12,441 --> 01:17:15,945
- GO AHEAD.  LOOK THAT UP
  IN THE CONSTITUTION.
- MAX, SHUT UP.

1269
01:17:15,945 --> 01:17:17,947
BRETT, HE'S NOT GUILTY.

1270
01:17:17,947 --> 01:17:20,950
BUT HE'S RESPONSIBLE, MAN.
COME ON.

1271
01:17:20,950 --> 01:17:25,955
LET ME TELL YOU, THE BEST SOAP
IN THE WORLD WON'T WASH THE SCUM
OFF THIS GUY'S HANDS.

1272
01:17:26,455 --> 01:17:29,959
I PROMISE.
LET ME ENLIGHTEN YOU, AVERY,

1273
01:17:29,959 --> 01:17:34,964
ABOUT YOUR NEW FRIEND
HERE CHARLIE; ABOUT WHAT
HE'S REALLY LIKE.

1274
01:17:34,964 --> 01:17:37,967
YOU WANT TO TELL HIM ABOUT
THE DOGS OR SHOULD I ?

1275
01:17:37,967 --> 01:17:39,969
NO, YOU'RE DOING GOOD.

1276
01:17:40,469 --> 01:17:41,971
JUMP IN ANY TIME.

1277
01:17:42,471 --> 01:17:45,474
ABOUT A YEAR AGO,
CHARLIE HAD A HOUSE IN JERSEY.

1278
01:17:45,975 --> 01:17:49,478
HE MOVES IN.  NEXT-DOOR
NEIGHBORS HAVE DOGS.  TWO DOGS ?
THEY'RE BARKIN' ALL NIGHT LONG.

1279
01:17:49,478 --> 01:17:53,983
CHARLIE GOES OVER, THE NICE GUY
THAT HE IS, ASKED THEM
TO KEEP THE NOISE DOWN.

1280
01:17:53,983 --> 01:17:59,488
NEXT NIGHT AFTER THAT, SAME
FUCKIN' DOGS-- BARK, BARK, BARK.
ALL FUCKIN' NIGHT LONG.

1281
01:17:59,488 --> 01:18:02,491
NEXT NIGHT AFTER THAT
AND THE NEXT NIGHT AFTER THAT,
UNTIL ONE NIGHT--

1282
01:18:02,992 --> 01:18:04,994
NOTHIN' MAN.
SILENCE.

1283
01:18:04,994 --> 01:18:08,381
[ Chuckles ]
NO MORE NOISE.

1284
01:18:08,381 --> 01:18:12,885
COPS GOT THERE ABOUT A WEEK
LATER.  THE DOGS WERE FINE.
HAPPIER THAN PIGS IN SHIT,

1285
01:18:12,885 --> 01:18:15,388
MUNCHIN' ON TOP SIRLOIN.

1286
01:18:15,388 --> 01:18:18,391
THE NEIGHBORS--
AVERY, THE NEIGHBORS--
THEY NEVER FUCKIN' FOUND.

1287
01:18:18,391 --> 01:18:22,395
OKAY ?  GONE.
HOW AM I DOIN', CHARLIE ?
IS THAT ABOUT RIGHT ?

1288
01:18:22,895 --> 01:18:27,900
-ALMOST.
-BET THAT WAS A RUMOR.  HE'S NOT
 INVOLVED WITH THE MOB ANYMORE.

1289
01:18:27,900 --> 01:18:30,903
OH, GIVE ME A FUCKIN' BREAK !
HOW DO YOU THINK HE WAS ABLE...

1290
01:18:30,903 --> 01:18:33,406
TO FIND YOUR SISTER
WITH ONE PHONE CALL ?

1291
01:18:33,406 --> 01:18:36,409
COINCIDENCE ?
COME ON.

1292
01:18:39,412 --> 01:18:42,415
YOUR FRIEND IS RIGHT.
IT'S NOT A COINCIDENCE.

1293
01:18:42,415 --> 01:18:44,917
I WAS ABLE TO CONTACT
THE RIGHT PEOPLE,
THE WAY YOU COUNTED ON.

1294
01:18:44,917 --> 01:18:49,422
IT'S A GOOD THING FOR YOU
THAT I AM WHO I AM AND I DO
WHAT I DO AND I KNOW WHO I KNOW,

1295
01:18:49,422 --> 01:18:53,926
OTHERWISE, YOUR PRINCESS
WOULD BE CHOPPED UP
AND IN THE BLENDER BY NOW.

1296
01:18:53,926 --> 01:18:58,431
I'LL TELL YOU SOMETHIN' ELSE:
EVEN AFTER WHAT YOU DID TO ME,
I KEPT MY PART OF THE BARGAIN.

1297
01:18:58,931 --> 01:19:03,436
NO MORE.
WHO DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE DEALING WITH ?

1298
01:19:03,936 --> 01:19:09,442
GUESS AGAIN.  YOU WANT TO KNOW
WHAT ELSE I COULD DO
WITH ONE PHONE CALL ?

1299
01:19:09,442 --> 01:19:14,447
HOW ABOUT I HAVE YOUR ASS
MADE INTO MINCEMEAT ?

1300
01:19:14,447 --> 01:19:16,949
I'LL TELL YOU WHAT IN FACT
HAPPENED WITH MY NEIGHBORS.

1301
01:19:16,949 --> 01:19:19,452
IT'S GOT NOTHING TO DO
WITH BARKING DOGS.

1302
01:19:19,452 --> 01:19:23,456
THAT FAMILY, WAY BACK,
DID SOMETHING...

1303
01:19:23,456 --> 01:19:26,459
VICIOUSTO MINE.

1304
01:19:26,959 --> 01:19:29,462
EVERYTHING YOUR PAL BRETT
SAID IS TRUE,

1305
01:19:29,462 --> 01:19:31,964
EXCEPT HE LEFT OUT
ONE DETAIL:

1306
01:19:32,465 --> 01:19:34,467
THOSE DOGS--

1307
01:19:34,467 --> 01:19:38,471
IT WAS NOT STEAK
THEY WERE EATING.

1308
01:19:40,973 --> 01:19:43,976
[ Thunder Rumbling ]

1309
01:19:43,976 --> 01:19:47,480
[ Pager Beeping ]

1310
01:19:47,480 --> 01:19:49,982
GUYS, IT'S FOR HIM.

1311
01:19:50,483 --> 01:19:52,485
CHARLIE, YOU THERE ?

1312
01:19:52,985 --> 01:19:56,489
[ Charlie ]  YEAH.
[ Marty ]  GOOD NEWS:  THE TERMS
HAVE BEEN OFFERED AND ACCEPTED.

1313
01:19:56,489 --> 01:19:59,492
THESE GUYS ARE GONNA MAKE SURE
THE MONEY IS IN PLAY,
THAT I'M GONE...

1314
01:19:59,992 --> 01:20:03,496
AND NOBODY'S WATCHING US,
AND THEN THEY'RE GONNA
DROP THE GIRL OFF...

1315
01:20:03,496 --> 01:20:06,499
AT THE EMERGENCY ROOM
 AT THE LENNOX HILL HOSPITAL.

1316
01:20:06,999 --> 01:20:09,502
YOU GOT THAT ?
I'LL BE FRONTING YOU THE MONEY.
I KNOW YOU'RE GOOD FOR IT.

1317
01:20:09,502 --> 01:20:14,006
REMEMBER, THE BANKS
DON'T OPEN TILL 10:00,
SO DON'T GO DYING ON ME.

1318
01:20:14,006 --> 01:20:17,009
REMEMBER, I'M A LAWYER.
I GOT FRIENDS IN HELL.

1319
01:20:17,009 --> 01:20:19,512
SO, WHAT ?
IS IT STILL A GO,
OR WHAT ?

1320
01:20:20,012 --> 01:20:22,014
ONE SECOND.

1321
01:20:24,517 --> 01:20:27,520
YOU WANNA PLAY... STILL ?

1322
01:20:27,520 --> 01:20:30,523
GOOD.

1323
01:20:30,523 --> 01:20:33,025
NOW WE PLAY MY WAY.

1324
01:20:35,027 --> 01:20:38,531
I GIVE MY FRIEND THE GO-AHEAD.
YOU TELL HIM WHERE WE ARE.

1325
01:20:38,531 --> 01:20:42,034
I WANT MY OWN DRIVER
WAITING OUTSIDE THAT DOOR.

1326
01:20:42,034 --> 01:20:45,037
SO'S YOU GOT NO OPPORTUNITY
WHATSOEVER--

1327
01:20:45,538 --> 01:20:47,540
CRAP OUT
ON YOUR PART OF THIS.

1328
01:20:47,540 --> 01:20:53,045
- FORGET IT.  YOU'RE GOING
  TO HAVE TO TRUST US.
- NO.  YOU TRUST ME.

1329
01:20:56,549 --> 01:20:59,552
WELL, HOW 'BOUT
SOMETHING NEARBY ?

1330
01:20:59,552 --> 01:21:02,054
- YEAH, NOT HERE.
- A HOTEL.

1331
01:21:02,054 --> 01:21:04,557
YEAH, GOOD.

1332
01:21:05,558 --> 01:21:08,561
HMM ?

1333
01:21:10,563 --> 01:21:14,066
RESTAURANT.  GAS STATION.

1334
01:21:18,571 --> 01:21:20,573
NO COMMENT ?

1335
01:21:25,077 --> 01:21:27,079
MARTY,
CALL THE WHOLE THING OFF.

1336
01:21:27,079 --> 01:21:31,083
- NO.  NO, PLEASE.
- MIDDLEBURY INN.

1337
01:21:31,083 --> 01:21:35,087
IT'S A HALF-MILE AWAY.
IT'S IN MONTAUK.
IT'S GOT A COFFEE SHOP.

1338
01:21:35,087 --> 01:21:37,590
MIDDLEBURY INN.
MONTAUK.  GOT THAT ?

1339
01:21:37,590 --> 01:21:41,594
- THE MIDDLEBURY INN.
  OKAY, SO HOW DO I GET THERE ?
- HOW DO YOU GET THERE ?

1340
